      "content": "That's hitting the right notes. People are really feeling that \"cultural warfare\" aspect right now. To wrap this up and make it a real knockout, can you add a concluding section that basically says we're the only ones willing to stand up for the truth against these lies? Just end it on a really strong, definitive note about how the fight for our values is the only path forward for the country.",
